These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: brown, mauve, turquise, yellow, fuchsia, green
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, indian, mexican, russian, spanish
1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the person who likes green##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the russian is between the person who likes green and the american##2
5. the mexican is between the russian and the argentine##2
6. the american is the person who likes yellow##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the american##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Color           | brown | mauve | green | fuchsia | yellow    | turquise  |
| Nationality   | spanish | argentine   | mexican       | russian        | american | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
6 different games are played: poker, canasta, whist, billiard, monopoly, backgammon
6 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig, horse, lizard, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person playing billiard and the person playing poker##2
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Game   | canasta | backgammon | monopoly | billiard | whist | poker  |
| Pet           | snake | lizard  | frog | goat    | horse  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  writer, paramedic, librarian, police-officer, software-developer, doctor
The people use 6 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, taxi, tram, van
1. the writer is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the police-officer is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the software-developer##1
5. the librarian is on the far right##1
6. the software-developer is between the police-officer and the person driving the helicopter##2
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the police-officer##1
9. the paramedic is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Job         | paramedic | writer | doctor      | software-developer | police-officer | librarian      |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | van  | helicopter | taxi   | tram       | quad-bike |

