.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, soy-milk, coffee, cola, fanta
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the roller is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the person drinking fanta##2
7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Beverage        | juice    | fanta | soy-milk | milk | cola | coffee   |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi        | quad-bike  | bike     | trike  | roller |

