.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, orange, black, emerald, apricot, pink
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, cycling, golf, ice-hockey, soccer
1. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes black and the person who likes apricot##2
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
8. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Color   | red   | emerald    | pink | black | orange | apricot   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | badminton | cycling | soccer | golf  | biathlon |

