.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There 6 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, nectarine, orange, pepper, strawberry
6 different games are played: chess, monopoly, poker, backgammon, canasta, go
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing go is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
4. the person playing go is on the far right##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
6. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person playing poker is the person eating strawberry##1
8. the person eating nectarine is between the person eating orange and the person playing go##2
9. the person eating cauliflower is the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Food    | cauliflower | strawberry | pepper  | orange      | nectarine | grapefruit  |
| Game   | monopoly  | poker    | backgammon | chess | canasta | go |

