The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, roller, tram, van
1. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing canasta is between the person playing go and the person playing domino##2
4. the person playing domino is the person driving the van##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
6. the person playing go is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the tram##2
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
9. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Game       | snooker | domino | canasta | go | monopoly | bridge |
| Transport   | quad-bike | van    | tram  | bike    | roller    | boat    |

