1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to london##2
4. the musician is the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the mechanic is between the journalist and the social-worker##2
6. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
9. the mechanic is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Job           | musician | teacher | social-worker | mechanic | journalist | designer |
| City   | liverpool   | colone   | rome         | london    | boston     | new-york     |

