.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, gardening, hiking, singing, sudoku
6 different games are played: go, bridge, mah-jongg, backgammon, monopoly, poker
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the person playing go is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person playing poker##2
 3. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person playing go##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | chess   | singing  | filmmaking | hiking | sudoku | gardening     |
| Game   | bridge | go | poker    | monopoly | backgammon | mah-jongg |

