.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, frog, hedgehog, rabbit, snake
House: townhouse, art-deco, gothic-revival, tower, cottage, futuristic
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the tower house##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is the cottage house##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the right of the tower house##1
 4. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
 5. the cottage house is between the art-deco house and the owner of the frog##2
 6. the tower house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 7. the townhouse house is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the townhouse house##1
 9. the owner of the cat is between the townhouse house and the owner of the chinchilla##2
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | snake   | rabbit | frog       | hedgehog | cat    | chinchilla |
| House   | art-deco | cottage  | gothic-revival | townhouse      | tower | futuristic        |

