.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-13::.
There 6 different types of food: apple, cherry, cranberry, kale, peas, pineapple
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, april, december, january, november, may
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person eating peas and the person eating kale##2
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person eating apple##1
8. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Food          | cranberry | cherry | apple | peas    | pineapple | kale |
| Birthday   | december     | may | january   | april | march | november |

