There are 6 different favourite colors: yellow, ivory, ebony, turquise, apricot, fuchsia
The people have 6 different jobs:  dancer, paramedic, photographer, pilot, scientist, security-guard
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 2. the security-guard is between the scientist and the person who likes ivory##2
 3. the scientist is between the person who likes fuchsia and the dancer##2
 4. the photographer is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is between the photographer and the person who likes ebony##2
 6. the person who likes turquise is the paramedic##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 8. the pilot is on the right of the paramedic##1
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
10. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Color   | turquise     | yellow | apricot   | ebony     | fuchsia       | ivory       |
| Job    | paramedic | pilot   | dancer | scientist | security-guard | photographer |

