.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, disco, metal, pop, r&b, trance
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, november, july, august, january, october
 1. the fan of trance is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 4. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the fan of metal is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the fan of pop is the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | trance | r&b    | metal     | disco      | pop    | classical |
| Birthday   | november | september | january | july | october | august  |

