.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, collecting, cooking, drawing, rock-climbing, woodworking
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: aconite, bellflower, daffodil, begonia, sunflower, zinnia
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is camping##2
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Hobby         | drawing | camping | collecting | woodworking | rock-climbing | cooking |
| Flower   | aconite | sunflower | daffodil      | begonia     | zinnia       | bellflower |

 